India’s Inflation May Slow to 7% by 2011-End, ING’s Condon Says

-- B y   U n n i   K r i s h n a n
-- 
2011-09-20T05:12:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/india-s-inflation-may-slow-to-7-by-2011-end-ing-s-condon-says.html
India ’s inflation may slow to 7
percent by the end of this year or the beginning of 2012,  Tim
Condon , head of Asia research at ING Groep NV in  Singapore , said
in an interview to Bloomberg UTV television channel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
